                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Rockhill</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <hi rend="italic">
                            <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-12-18">December 18, 1906</date>
                        </hi>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Rockhill reports that he has been informed by the foreign office that,
                    according to the agreement with the Russian minister, the three cities, Kirin,
                    Harbin, Manchuria, will be opened to international residence and trade January
                    14, 1907.)</p>
            </div>
